title: ContextClues
---
That looks like a wataboshi, a traditional cotton hood used in Shinto marriges for the bride.
===


title: Waraji
---
Those are Waraji, a pair of straw woven sandals. 
===

title: Kanzashi
---
That's a kanzashi, a traditional hair ornament. 
===

title: Omamori
---
It looks like he is carrying an omamori, a traditional good luck charm.
